## Adding a feature

```
lib/features/<feature>/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ data/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ <feature>_repository.dart    # talks to Dio via ref.read(apiClientProvider)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ domain/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ <feature>.dart               # models, value objects (pure)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ presentation/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ <feature>_screen.dart        # ConsumerWidget
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ <feature>_controller.dart    # @riverpod AsyncNotifier
```

Then register the route in `lib/core/router/router.dart`.

Every interactive widget needs a stable `Key('<feature>_<purpose>')` вЂ” the
test-specialist's Appium specs target by `Key`, not by visible text. Adding
a widget without a `Key` is a defect.

